snippet.title: Scribblenauts Unmasked: A DC Comics Adventure Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Scribblenauts Unmasked: A DC Comics Adventure is officially available for purchase! Get it on the Nintendo Wii U, Nintendo 3DS and PC! http://bit.ly/Get-Scribblenauts-Unmasked

Super power your imagination and join Maxwell and thousands of DC Comics characters on epic adventures through the entire DC Comics universe!
